abstract: >-
  A complete bioinformatics pipeline for RNA-seq data analysis, from initial 
  quantification through genotype/phenotype processing and QTL input preparation. 
  The pipeline integrates multiple tools and analysis steps into a unified 
  command-line interface, enabling allele-specific expression analysis, genotype 
  calling from transcript mapping data, and automated QTL analysis preparation.
